Mandatory :
- Cylinder object
- Turning using keybinds locks rotation at given point ~180 degree
- Projected shadows
	- Diffused projected shadows
- Set a MAX_OBJS macro, "setable" via -D compile flag. This macro has to
be ckecked inside the parsing.
- Set a BLUR_LVL macro, "setable" via -D compile flag. It has to check that
the flag is set in a valid range (at least 1, but max ?)
default would be (WIDTH * HEIGHT / 1000000) ?

Bonus :
- Checker pattern
- Bumping texture
- Phong lightening
- Cone object / Torus object

Bonus ++ :
- Handle mouse for camera
- Handle key pressed and released for movements

- Using mouse click to edit properties of the aimed object.

- Transparency of the object
- Mate or shady surface

- Show coordinates on screen

- Cube object
- Klein bottle
- Mobius band

- One mirrored plane

- Print a message on program startup with keybinds

- Bind the scroll wheel for editing the FOV. Ranging from ]0:180]
	- Check that the FOV is parsed as an 8bit int

sdemey :
- Handle color with light
- Fix specular and diffuse reflection

mmichele :
- Fix camera rotations
- Handle camera movements properly, like FPS
- Minor visual fix on blur tracing
	- Enhance blur tracing by make it more to less blurry with time
	- Not recalculate fine pixels that were previously calculated when blur tracing
